tch%20a%20movie%20with%20no%20problem%2C%20but%20actually%20living%20in%20the%20US%20was%20a%20heightened%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Columbia%20grad%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d19d8957d362d375e8a163%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20graduated%20from%20Columbia%20University.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20graduating%2C%20Columbia%20University%20held%20a%20job%20fair.%20International%20students%20were%20warned%20that%20it'd%20be%20hard%20to%20get%20hired%20because%20sponsoring%20visas%20was%20expensive%20for%20employers.%20I%20went%20with%20little%20to%20no%20hope%2C%20and%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20a%20television%20network%20hired%20me%20right%20there%20and%20then.%20When%20I%20raised%20my%20concerns%20about%20being%20on%20a%20visa%2C%20they%20let%20me%20know%20that%20they'd%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-memos-sent-big-tech-trump-h-1b-changes-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eapplying%20for%20my%20H-1B%3C%2Fa%3E%20right%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281df785c-3214-427a-b126-1d206feb209b%5C%22%3EI%20was%20on%20an%20H-1B%20visa%20for%206%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20that%20hired%20me%20had%20its%20own%20legal%20team%20in-house%20that%20was%20incredibly%20well-versed%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh1b-visa-trump-executive-order-what-to-know-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20visas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20handled%20the%20whole%20laborious%20process%20for%20me%2C%20and%20I%20was%20approved%20within%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20catch%20was%20that%20if%20I%20wanted%20or%20needed%20to%20change%20employers%2C%20a%20new%20company%20had%20to%20re-sponsor%20me.%20I%20felt%20somewhat%20tied%20to%20that%20job%2C%20especially%20because%20every%20time%20I%20applied%20to%20a%20new%20role%2C%20I%20would%20get%20asked%20the%20same%20question%2C%20%26quot%3BWill%20you%20need%20sponsoring%20in%20the%20future%3F%26quot%3B%20which%20almost%20immediately%20meant%20a%20rejection%20was%20coming%20my%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20posing%20for%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d19cf4f9db348adc0bf0ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221506%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20changed%20jobs%20during%20her%20H-1B%20visa.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20at%20that%20job%20for%20two%20years%20of%20my%20three-year%20max%20before%20needing%20to%20have%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-h-1b-visa-fee-silicon-valley-tech-hiring-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EH-1B%20visa%20renewed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20I%20found%20another%20role%20at%20a%20different%20company%20that%20was%20more%20interesting%20to%20me%2C%20I%20applied%2C%20disclosing%20that%20I%20had%20a%20work%20visa%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20transferred%20and%20eventually%20renewed.%20Being%20trilingual%20%E2%80%94%20I%20am%20fluent%20in%20Spanish%2C%20Portuguese%2C%20and%20English%20%E2%80%94%20played%20in%20my%20favor%20because%20they%20were%20looking%20for%20someone%20to%20explore%20taking%20the%20company%20into%20Latin%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20nerve-racking%20because%20there's%20always%20a%20chance%20that%20your%20visa%20will%20be%20denied%2C%20the%20initial%20transfer%20and%20following%20renewal%20process%20went%20smoothly.%20I%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-us-buenos-aires-taylor-swift-concert-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20to%20Argentina%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20to%20get%20my%20visa%20restamped%20with%20my%20new%20employer's%20name%20on%20it%20and%20undergo%20extensive%