Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoetzmann%20advises%20staying%20invested%20long-term%20for%20better%20returns%2C%20despite%20market%20fears.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYale%20economist%20William%20Goetzmann%20has%20felt%20the%20fear%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-all-time-highs-sp500-recession-jobs-report-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estock-market%20crash%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20strike%20into%20an%20investor.%20He's%20lived%20through%20at%20least%20four%20of%20them%3A%201987%2C%202000%2C%202008%2C%20and%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20watched%20my%20entire%20life%20savings%20drop%20by%2050%25%20during%20the%20crash%20of%202008%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Americans%20who%20had%20money%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20at%20the%20time%20saw%20similar%20losses.%20It's%20the%20kind%20of%20scarring%20experience%20that%20can%20make%20an%20investor%20paranoid%20that%20another%20crash%20is%20always%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20apparently%20has%2C%20as%20Goetzmann's%20research%20has%20found%20that%20fear%20of%20a%20rapid%20decline%20is%20pervasive%20among%20investors.%20Since%202000%2C%20respondents%20to%20Goetzmann's%20surveys%20at%20any%20given%20time%20have%20generally%20said%20there's%20a%2010%25-20%25%20chance%20of%20a%20crash%20in%20the%20next%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22black%20tuesday%2C%20wall%20street%20crash%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F55004a5d6da811a06682c541%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221472%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECrowd%20gathering%20on%20Wall%20Street%20in%20New%20York%20after%20the%20Wall%20Street%20crash%20late%20October%201929.%3Cp%3EAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20our%20research%20suggests%20is%20they%20can%20be%20reacting%20to%20even%20things%20that%20aren't%20having%20to%20do%20with%20the%20stock%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BLike%20if%20there's%20a%20big%20earthquake%20nearby%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20think%20there's%20a%20higher%20probability%20of%20a%20crash.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20there%20seem%20to%20be%20heightened%20fears%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-gigantic-price-bubble-sp500-negative-returns-rosenberg-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20market%20bubble%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20subsequent%20pop%20%E2%80%94%20with%20AI%20stocks%20fueling%20an%2086%25%20surge%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20Shiller%20CAPE%20ratio%20at%20its%20third-highest%20level%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20concerns%20are%20understandable%20in%20some%20sense%2C%20they%20also%20defy%20the%20data%2C%20Goetzmann%20said.%20His%20research%20has%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-when-how-to-buy-the-dip-schwab-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estock%20crashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20big%20surges%20don't%20happen%20all%20that%20often%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20and%20when%20they%20do%20occur%2C%20they%20don't%20last%20that%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202016%20paper%2C%20Goetzmann%20looked%20at%20instances%20around%20the%20world%20since%20the%201880s%20when%20a%20country's%20market%20has%20surged%20by%20100%25%20over%20a%20one-year%20period%20or%20a%20three-year%20period.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20stocks%20have%20ended%20up%20down%20by%20at%20least%2050%25%20in%20the%20following%20year%20or%20five-year%20period%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20the%20time.%20In%20fact%2C%2026%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20market%20has%20risen%20another%20100%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20trader%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20stock%20index%20futures%20pit%20at%20the%20Chicago%20Board%20of%20Trade%20reads%20a%20newspaper%20before%20the%20start%20of%20trading%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61ade6c2983f360019c8838e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22727%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20trader%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20stock%20index%20futures%20pit%20at%20the%20Chicago%20Board%20of%20Trade%20reads%20a%20newspaper%20before%20the%20start%20of%20trading%20on%20October%2010%2C%202008.%3Cp%3EScott%20Olson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20Goetzmann's%20research%20is%20narrow%20and%20doesn't%20account%20for%20all%20downside%20scenarios.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20account%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20roughly%2049%25%20in%20the%20two%20years%20after%20the%20dot-com%20bust%20from%202000-2002%2C%20as%20the%20market%20was%20down%20about%2018%25%20in%202005%2C%20five%20years%20after%20its%20peak.%20Yet%20this%20is%20widely%20looked%20at%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20damaging%20crashes%20in%20market%20history%2C%20as%20it%20took%20investors%20years%20to%20claw%20back%20the%20deepest%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20doesn't%20account%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20crashes%20tend%20to%20arrive%20alongside%20recessions%2C%20and%20those%20who%20end%20up%20unemployed%20may%20be%20forced%20to%20sell%20their%20stock%20holdings%20near%20the%20bottom%20to%20meet%20liquidity%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20have%20a%20long-term%20time%20horizon%20and%20are%20able%20to%20stay%20invested%2C%20Goetzmann's%20message%20is%20simple%3A%20even%20if%20the%20market%20crashes%2C%20it's%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20vast%20swaths%20of%20your%20wealth%20will%20be%20gone%20if%20you%20just%20ride%20it%20out%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20wait%20five%20years%20after%20this%20event%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20better%20off.%20That's%20what%20I'm%20telling%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20can%20say%2C%20'Look%2C%20we're%20a%20small%20college%20endowment%2C%20and%20we%20depend%20on%20our%20endowment%20to%20pay%20the%20salaries%20of%20all%20the%20staff%2C%20so%20I%20just%20can't%20wait%20five%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20Goetzmann%20is%20worried%20that%20investors'%20fearfulness%20is%20getting%20worse%2C%20which%20will%20keep%20people%20out%20of%20the%20market%20and%20rob%20them%20of%20future%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20day%20and%20age%2C%20we're%20being%20shocked%20all%20the%20time%20when%20we%20get%20on%20the%20internet%20or%20watch%20television%20with%20scary%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20one%20concern%20that%20I%20have%20is%20that%20if%20people%20are%20generally%20more%20fearful%20of%20a%20terrible%20event%2C%20they%20might%20be%20more%20fearful%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20crashing%20as%20well%2C%20and%20they%20might%20not%20even%20invest%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThey%20might%20say%2C%20'Well%2C%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20sidelines%20because%20the%20bottom%20could%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20tomorrow%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20any%20savings%20left.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20hat%20and%20suit%20stands%20beside%20his%20car%20with%20a%20sign%20that%20reads%20%26quot%3B%24100.%20Will%20buy%20this%20car.%20Must%20have%20cash.%20Lost%20all%20on%20the%20stock%20market.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bcc227b4912df3ae1b8fa2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeveral%20people%20faced%20losses%20during%20the%20stock%20market%20crash%2C%20making%20the%20once%20accessible%20luxuries%2C%20once%20again%2C%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20several%20people.%3Cp%3EBettmann%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Goetzmann%20himself%20knows%20the%20benefits%20of%20taking%20a%20calm%20approach%20and%20staying%20invested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20four%20crashes%20Goetzmann%20has%20seen%2C%20he's%20kept%20his%20money%20in%20the%20market%2C%20eventually%20benefiting%20from%20the%20long%20bull-market%20surges%20that%20have%20followed%20steep%20declines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20spring%20was%20quite%20scary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20held%20my%20breath%20and%20just%20said%2C%20'Well%2C%20I'll%20stick%20with%20what%20the%20long-term%20data%20show%20us%20about%20the%20stock%20market.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-why-you-shouldnt-be-scared-yale-goetzmann-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758618901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d174cb183847aa39d73822%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-why-you-shouldnt-be-scared-yale-goetzmann-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yale%20economist%20William%20Goetzmann%20says%20investors%20are%20generally%20too%20worried%20about%20a%20market%20crash%2C%20and%20the%20best%20move%20is%20to%20stay%20invested%20through%20the%20volatility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-why-you-shouldnt-be-scared-yale-goetzmann-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maha%20shocker%3A%20BJP%20workers%20make%20Cong%20leader%20wear%20sari%20over%20PM%20photo%3B%20oppn%20fumes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758618819000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-124066774%2Cimgsize-2035443.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fthane%2Fmaharashtra-shocker-bjp-workers-make-con