20environments%20let%20me%20leverage%20my%20skills%20fully%20and%20communicate%20my%20needs%20more%20clearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20painful%20when%20people%20see%20disability%20or%20neurodivergence%20as%20less%20than%2C%20but%20the%20stigmas%20reflect%20a%20system%20that%20hasn't%20caught%20up%2C%20not%20our%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20autistic%2C%20ADHD%2C%20partially%20blind%2C%20queer%2C%20and%20Vietnamese%20American%20from%20a%20low-income%20household%20isn't%20something%20to%20hide%3B%20it's%20what%20makes%20me%20who%20I%20am.%20What%20once%20felt%20like%20a%20weakness%20has%20become%20my%20superpower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20being%20neurodiverse%20in%20tech%3F%20Contact%20the%20editor%20Tess%20Martinelli%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atmartinelli%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Etmartinelli%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-autism-helped-me-break-into-tech-without-tech-degree-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758618661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d1ae45183847aa39d74021%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-autism-helped-me-break-into-tech-without-tech-degree-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dennis%20Tran%20says%20being%20autistic%20gave%20him%20an%20edge%20at%20breaking%20into%20a%20Quality%20Assurance%20tech%20job%20without%20a%20degree.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kaila%20Yu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-autism-helped-me-break-into-tech-without-tech-degree-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22European%20recognition%20of%20Palestinian%20state