of-world%2F9-places-on-earth-where-the-sun-never-sets-the-longest-days-in-the-world%2Famp_articleshow%2F124066415.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here%20are%20the%20jobs%20most%20and%20least%20likely%20to%20be%20transformed%20by%20GenAI%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20index%20from%20Indeed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222047%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20nurse%20and%20a%20software%20developer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cde7ed57d362d375e89060%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221384%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20nurse%20(left)%20and%20a%20software%20developer%20(right_%3Cp%3EImago%20Images%2FScience%20Photo%20Library%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJob-listings%20platform%2C%20Indeed%2C%20created%20a%20%26quot%3BGenAI%20Skill%20Transformation%20Index.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20index%20assesses%20how%20AI%20is%20affecting%202%2C900%20skills.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20chart%20below%20shows%20which%20jobs%20are%20being%20transformed%20the%20most%2C%20and%20which%20roles%20are%20unaffected.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-microsoft-openai-fight-standards-limit-ai-access-websites-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20steadily%20rewiring%20the%20DNA%20of%20work%2C%20radically%20transforming%20some%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-jobs-plunged-since-chatgpt-which-roles-boomed-indeed-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20other%20professions%20remain%20relatively%20immune.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20a%20new%20analysis%20from%20Indeed%2C%20a%20job-listings%20platform%2C%20that%20created%20an%20index%20to%20track%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-workers-use-ai-survey-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworkplace%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed's%20GenAI%20Skill%20Transformation%20Index%20measures%20how%20much%20generative%20AI%20could%20change%20the%20way%20different%20skills%20or%20jobs%20are%20performed.%20Instead%20of%20measuring%20whether%20this%20technology%20will%20fully%20replace%20human%20workers%2C%20it%20examines%20how%20skills%20may%20be%20applied%20going%20forward%20and%20how%20human%20involvement%20with%20those%20skills%20and%20tasks%20could%20evolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20and%20index%20assessed%20the%20cognitive%20and%20physical%20demands%20required%20across%20nearly%202%2C900%20work%20skills%20and%20the%20capacity%20of%20generative%20AI%20to%20perform%20them.%20Indeed%20focused%20on%20two%20particular%20criteria%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProblem-solving%20ability%3A%20The%20degree%20to%20which%20a%20skill%20requires%20cognitive%20reasoning%2C%20applied%20knowledge%2C%20and%20practical%20judgment%2C%20and%20how%20well%20generative%20AI%20can%20replicate%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhysical%20necessity%3A%20Whether%20a%20skill%20requires%20physical%20execution.%20Until%20general-purpose%20robotics%20advances%20significantly%2C%20these%20tasks%20remain%20mostly%20human-exclusive%2C%20according%20to%20Indeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20this%20evaluation%2C%20skills%20were%20grouped%20into%20four%20distinct%20categories%20based%20on%20their%20potential%20to%20be%20transformed%20by%20generative%20AI%3A%20minimal%20transformation%2C%20assisted%20transformation%2C%20hybrid%20transformation%2C%20and%20full%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1392c1b-3a99-4339-86eb-2fbd1bc00663%5C%22%3EKey%20findings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20framework%2C%20Indeed%20found%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E41%25%20of%20the%20almost%202%2C900%20common%20work%20skills%20assessed%20are%20exposed%20to%20the%20highest%20potential%20levels%20of%20GenAI-driven%20transformation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMore%20than%20a%20quarter%20(26%25)%20of%20jobs%20posted%20on%20Indeed%20in%20the%20past%20year%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bhighly%26quot%3B%20transformed%20by%20GenAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20majority%20(54%25)%20of%20jobs%20posted%20on%20Indeed%20in%20the%20past%20year%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bmoderately%26quot%3B%20transformed%2C%20and%20their%20evolution%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20quickly%20businesses%20adopt%20GenAI%20and%20how%20well%20workers%20adapt%20and%20reskill.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAlmost%20half%20(46%25)%20of%20skills%20in%20a%20typical%20US%20job%20posting%20are%20poised%20for%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%20transformation%26quot%3B%20by%20GenAI.%20Human%20oversight%20will%20remain%20critical%20when%20applying%20these%20skills%2C%20but%20GenAI%20can%20already%20perform%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20routine%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20occupations%2C%20including%20software%20development%2C%20are%20more%20highly%20exposed.%20Roles%20requiring%20more%20physical%20presence%20and%20human%20interaction%2C%20including%20nursing%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20less%20impacted%2C%20with%20GenAI%20primarily%20changing%20administrative%20tasks%20but%20not%20necessarily%20the%20core%20parts%20of%20these%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Indeed%20ran%20an%20initial%20version%20of%20this%20analysis%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20no%20skills%20were%20rated%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20likely%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20fully%20replaced%20by%20GenAI.%20Today%2C%2019%20skills%20(0.7%25%20of%20all%20skills%20analyzed)%20were%20assessed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bvery%20likely%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20fully%20replaced%20by%20GenAI%2C%20still%20small%20in%20absolute%20terms%2C%20but%20a%20significant%20signal%20of%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenAI%20has%20gotten%20(and%20continues%20to%20get)%20smarter%2C%26quot%3B%20Annina%20Hering%2C%20senior%20economist%20at%20Indeed's%20Hiring%20Lab%2C%20and%20Arcenis%20Rojas%2C%20a%20data%20scientist%20at%20the%20lab%2C%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20physical%20execution%20is%20not%20required%20%E2%80%94%20an%20admittedly%20big%20caveat%20%E2%80%94%20and%20GenAI%20capabilities%20continue%20to%20grow%2C%20more%20skills%20are%20likely%20to%20cross%20the%20threshold%20into%20realistic%20automation%20as%20work%20continues%20to%20evolve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da0f034f-23c3-48f2-8197-76cbd3a7c4c6%5C%22%3EThe%20outlook%20for%20different%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20findings%20reveal%20that%20childcare%2C%20nursing%2C%20and%20construction%20are%20the%20least%20likely%20to%20be%20transformed%20by%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20software%20development%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20transformed%20by%20generative%20AI.%20Eighty-one%20percent%20of%20the%20skills%20involved%20in%20these%20jobs%20will%20experience%20a%20hybrid%20transformation%20in%20which%20GenAI%20leads%20and%20humans%20provide%20oversight%2C%20according%20to%20Indeed's%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20%26amp%3B%20Analytics%20and%20accounting%20were%20second%20and%20third%2C%20behind%20software%20development%2C%20as%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20transformed%20by%20GenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20message%20is%20pretty%20blunt%3A%20no%20job%20is%20entirely%20immune%2C%20but%20not%20all%20jobs%20are%20equally%20exposed.%20Technical%20and%20information-heavy%20roles%20will%20feel%20the%20brunt%20of%20automation%2C%20while%20jobs%20grounded%20in%20physical%20presence%20and%20human%20touch%20will%20remain%20mostly%20shielded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20businesses%2C%20that%20means%20redesigning%20workflows%20and%20training%20pipelines.%20For%20workers%2C%20it%20means%20leaning%20into%20uniquely%20human%20strengths%2C%20such%20as%20physical%20dexterity%2C%20informed%20oversight%2C%20and%20empathy%2C%20that%20AI%20still%20can't%20replicate%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20full%20breakdown%20of%20jobs%20and%20skills%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22714%5C%22%20alt%3D%5